ViewObject.Name: TitleManufacturingView
ViewObject.SQLQuery: SELECT Title.ID, TitleRecord.ID AS ID1, Title.CONTENT_OWNER_ID, Title.TARGET_TRACKING_NO, Title.LONG_TITLE, Title.CATALOG_NUMBER, Title.CHECK_IN_REQUIREMENTS, TitleRecord.OVR_ID, TitleRecord.PM_TITLE, TitleRecord.QUALIFIER, TitleRecord.CONTENT_SOURCE, TitleRecord.PMID, TitleRecord.MANUFACTURING_PROCESS, TitleRecord.IMAGE_STORAGE, TitleRecord.JOURNAL_CODE, Title.SHORT_TITLE, ContentOwner.NAME Content_owner, ContentOwner.SITE, ( select count(content_owner_id) from trax_content_owner_title cot where cot.title_id = Title.id) content_owner_count, Title.CATALOG_ROOT, TraxUlrichsTitle.ULRICHS_SERIAL_ID, Title.PUBLICATION_START_YEAR, Title.PUBLICATION_END_YEAR, Title.FILM_AVAILABILITY, Title.BIBLIOGRAPHIC_STATUS, Title.ORIGINAL_PUBLISHING_CO, Title.ORIGINAL_PLACE_OF_PUBLICATION, Title.ORIGINAL_DATES_OF_PUBLICATION, Title.PLACE_OF_PUBLICATION_CODE, Title.EXERCISING_RIGHTS, Title.NON_FILING_INDICATOR, Title.EDITION_STATEMENT, Title.ALPHA_RECORD_DATES, Title.PUB_YEAR_VOLUME_FORMATTED, Title.PUB_YEAR_VOLUME_UNFORMATTED, Title.CATALOGING_SOURCE_URL, Title.SERIAL_SUB_TYPE, Title.PUBLICATION_FREQUENCY, Title.ROUTING, Title.PRIMARY_PM_CLASS, Title.SECONDARY_PM_CLASS, Title.PRODUCT_LINE, cl.CLASSIFICATION_NUMBER primary_classification, cl.CLASSIFICATION_TYPE primary_classification_type, TitleSubject.SUBJECT_TYPE, TitleSubject.SUBJECT as primary_subject, Title.NEWSPAPER_EDITION_FILMED, Title.CONTENT_TYPE, Title.SUB_CONTENT_TYPE, Title.ENUMERATION, Title.NUMBER_OF_UNITS, Title.PEER_REVIEW_FLAG, Title.OPEN_ACCESS, Title.CREATED_BY, Title.CREATED_DATE, trunc(Title.CREATED_DATE) as created_by_search, Title.LAST_UPDATED_BY, Title.LAST_UPDATED_DATE, trunc(Title.LAST_UPDATED_DATE) as last_updatedby_search, TraxUlrichsTitle.ID AS ULRICHS_ID FROM TRAX_TITLE Title LEFT OUTER JOIN TRAX_TITLE_RECORD TitleRecord ON Title.ID = TitleRecord.TITLE_ID LEFT OUTER JOIN TRAX_CONTENT_OWNER ContentOwner ON Title.CONTENT_OWNER_ID = ContentOwner.ID LEFT OUTER JOIN TRAX_CLASSIFICATION cl ON cl.TITLE_ID = Title.ID AND PRIMARY_FLAG ='Y' LEFT OUTER JOIN TRAX_TITLE_SUBJECT TitleSubject ON Title.ID = TitleSubject.TITLE_ID AND TitleSubject.PRIMARY_FLAG = 'Y' LEFT OUTER JOIN TRAX_TITLE_ULRICHS_RELATION ttur INNER JOIN TRAX_ULRICHS_TITLE TraxUlrichsTitle ON ttur.ULRICHS_SERIAL_ID = TraxUlrichsTitle.ULRICHS_SERIAL_ID ON Title.ID = ttur.TITLE_ID WHERE Title.ACTIVE_FLAG = 'Y'
